te/20 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black gradient-text\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span>+</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] sm:text-xs lg:text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Products shipped</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 sm:p-6 text-center hover:border-white/20 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black gradient-text\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span></span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] sm:text-xs lg:text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Global offices</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 sm:p-6 text-center hover:border-white/20 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black gradient-text\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span></span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] sm:text-xs lg:text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Industries served</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 sm:p-6 text-center hover:border-white/20 transition\"><div class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black gradient-text\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span>%</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] sm:text-xs lg:text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Client retention</div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative mt-12 sm:mt-16 overflow-hidden border-y border-white/5 py-4\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 sm:gap-12 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"transform:none\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇬🇧</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Birmingham</span><span>· <!-- -->United Kingdom</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇵🇰</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Multan</span><span>· <!-- -->Pakistan</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Austin, TX</span><span>· <!-- -->United States</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇦🇪</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Dubai</span><span>· <!-- -->United Arab Emirates</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇬🇧</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Birmingham</span><span>· <!-- -->United Kingdom</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇵🇰</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Multan</span><span>· <!-- -->Pakistan</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Austin, TX</span><span>· <!-- -->United States</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇦🇪</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Dubai</span><span>· <!-- -->United Arab Emirates</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇬🇧</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Birmingham</span><span>· <!-- -->United Kingdom</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇵🇰</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Multan</span><span>· <!-- -->Pakistan</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Austin, TX</span><span>· <!-- -->United States</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"text-base\">🇦🇪</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Dubai</span><span>· <!-- -->United Arab Emirates</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground/40\">—</span></span></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:0% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"services\" class=\"relative py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]\"></span>What we do</div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">Four practices.<!-- --> <span class=\"gradient-text\">One delivery engine.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base sm:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Whether you need a custom AI assistant, a high-converting website, a SaaS platform or a full growth programme, our cross-functional teams in the UK, Pakistan, USA and Dubai plug into your business and ship like an in-house squad.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -top-20 -right-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground\">AI &amp; ML</span><span class=\"grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground group-hover:text-foreground group-hover:border-white/20 transition\">0<!-- -->1</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">AI &amp; Machine Learning</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[#FF53A9] font-medium\">Intelligent systems that learn, decide and ship value.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">From custom LLM applications and RAG pipelines to computer vision and predictive models, our AI practice helps businesses across the UK, Pakistan, USA and Dubai turn raw data into autonomous, revenue-driving products.</p><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Custom LLM Solutions</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Fine-tuned GPT &amp; Llama models for your domain.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">AI Chatbots &amp; Assistants</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Conversational agents that resolve tickets and qualify leads.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Prompt Engineering</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Reliable, evaluated prompt pipelines for production.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Computer Vision &amp; NLP</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">OCR, defect detection, classification and beyond.</div></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(64px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -top-20 -right-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground\">Web</span><span class=\"grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground group-hover:text-foreground group-hover:border-white/20 transition\">0<!-- -->2</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Web Development</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[#FF53A9] font-medium\">High-performance websites &amp; web apps engineered to convert.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">We design and build marketing sites, SaaS dashboards, e-commerce storefronts and headless CMS platforms using Next.js, React and modern edge infrastructure — optimised for SEO in Birmingham, Pakistan, the US and Dubai markets.</p><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Full-Stack Web Development</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Next.js, React, Node — production from day one.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">SaaS Platform Engineering</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Multi-tenant dashboards, billing, analytics.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Auth &amp; Identity</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">SSO, SAML, MFA, role-based access.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Python Backend &amp; APIs</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">FastAPI, Django, async workers, data pipelines.</div></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -top-20 -right-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/10 blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground\">Growth</span><span class=\"grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground group-hover:text-foreground group-hover:border-white/20 transition\">0<!-- -->3</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Digital Marketing</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[#FF53A9] font-medium\">Compounding growth across search, social and paid channels.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Our growth team runs data-driven SEO, paid media, content and CRO programmes tailored to local intent in the UK (Birmingham), Pakistan, USA and Dubai — so every pound, rupee and dirham works harder.</p><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Paid Advertising (PPC)</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Google, Meta, TikTok &amp; LinkedIn ads that scale.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Content Strategy &amp; SEO</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Editorial that ranks and converts.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://