s font-bold text-muted-foreground group-hover:text-foreground group-hover:border-white/20 transition\">0<!-- -->4</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Creative Services</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[#FF53A9] font-medium\">Brand systems and product design that earn attention.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Our designers craft brand identities, product UIs and motion systems that feel premium in every market we serve — from Birmingham startups to Dubai enterprises.</p><ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Brand &amp; Graphic Design</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Identity systems, guidelines, assets.</div></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-3 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid h-5 w-5 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check h-3 w-3 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></span><div><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Video Production</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Ads, explainers, social cuts, motion.</div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 rounded-3xl gradient-bg p-8 sm:p-10 text-white shadow-2xl glow-brand\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold\">Not sure where to start?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-white/80 max-w-xl\">Book a free 30-minute consultation. We&#x27;ll map your goals to the right practice and give you a clear, no-obligation roadmap.</p></div><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-[#136DFF] hover:scale-[1.03] transition shrink-0\">Book a free call <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:100% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"work\" class=\"relative py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute left-1/4 top-0 h-[28rem] w-[28rem] rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]/10 blur-[120px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[28rem] w-[28rem] rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/10 blur-[120px]\"></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medi