k h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg></a><div class=\"absolute left-5 top-5 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-black/30 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-md\">47× ROAS</div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 pb-6\"><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/70\">Paid Growth · Marketing</div><div class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Verve Studio</div></div></div><div class=\"p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Meta &amp; Google campaigns with funnel optimisation that scaled ROAS from 3× to 47×.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium text-muted-foreground backdrop-blur\">Meta Ads</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium text-muted-foreground backdrop-blur\">Google</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium text-muted-foreground backdrop-blur\">CRO</span></div><a class=\"group/btn inline-flex shrink-0 items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full gradient-bg px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105\" href=\"/portfolio#verve-studio\">View project<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/btn:translate-x-0.5 group-hover/btn:-translate-y-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl ring-1 ring-white/5\"></div></article></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:0% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"process\" class=\"relative py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]\"></span>How we work</div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">A proven five-step <span class=\"gradient-text\">delivery model.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base sm:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">From the first workshop to post-launch growth, every engagement follows the same transparent, milestone-driven process — so you always know what&#x27;s next.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-black gradient-text\">01</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Step <!-- -->1</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Discovery</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Deep research into your goals, users and positioning to uncover opportunities that drive long-term growth.</p><div class=\"hidden lg:grid absolute top-1/2 -right-3 z-10 h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-card/80 -translate-y-1/2\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-black gradient-text\">02</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Step <!-- -->2</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Strategy</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">A scalable roadmap aligned with branding, user experience and measurable business impact.</p><div class=\"hidden lg:grid absolute top-1/2 -right-3 z-10 h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-card/80 -translate-y-1/2\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-black gradient-text\">03</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Step <!-- -->3</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Design</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Premium interfaces crafted with motion, clarity and immersive visual systems that captivate.</p><div class=\"hidden lg:grid absolute top-1/2 -right-3 z-10 h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-card/80 -translate-y-1/2\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-black gradient-text\">04</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Step <!-- -->4</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Build</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Modern engineering with AI integrations, scalable architecture and production-ready performance.</p><div class=\"hidden lg:grid absolute top-1/2 -right-3 z-10 h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-card/80 -translate-y-1/2\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.93)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-black gradient-text\">05</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Step <!-- -->5</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold\">Launch</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Deployment, optimisation and continuous iteration focused on performance and growth metrics.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:0% 50% 0\"></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:100% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"relative py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-[30rem] w-[60rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/8 blur-[120px]\"></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]\"></span>Client stories</div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">Trusted by founders &amp;<!-- --> <span class=\"gradient-text\">enterprise teams alike.</span></h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><figure class=\"relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-8 w-8 text-[#FF53A9]/60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground/90\">“<!-- -->ClickTake rebuilt our entire stack and tripled our online revenue in just four months. They genuinely felt like an extension of our internal team.<!-- -->”</blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg\">SM</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Sarah Mitchell</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Founder, Lumen Commerce<!-- --> · <!-- -->London, UK</div></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(64px)\"><figure class=\"relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-8 w-8 text-[#FF53A9]/60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground/90\">“<!-- -->The AI automations they engineered save us over 30 hours every week. Exceptional execution, clean systems and incredible design taste.<!-- -->”</blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg\">JO</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold\">James O&#x27;Connor</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">CTO, Northwind<!-- --> · <!-- -->Manchester, UK</div></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><figure class=\"relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-8 w-8 text-[#FF53A9]/60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground/90\">“<!-- -->The best digital partner we&#x27;ve worked with. Strategy, branding, development and growth — all executed at an elite level.<!-- -->”</blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg\">AK</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Aisha Khan</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Marketing Director, Verve Studio<!-- --> · <!-- -->Birmingham, UK</div></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(64px)\"><figure class=\"relative h-full rounded-3xl glass p-8 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-8 w-8 text-[#FF53A9]/60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground/90\">“<!-- -->From brand identity to a fully custom booking platform, ClickTake handled everything end-to-end. Premium craft, delivered on deadline.<!-- -->”</blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full gradient-bg text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg\">AA</div><div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Aisha Al-Mansoori</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">COO, Hospitality group<!-- --> · <!-- -->Dubai, UAE</div></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:0% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"about\" class=\"relative py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]\"></span>About ClickTake</div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">A global team built to<!-- --> <span class=\"gradient-text\">take ideas to market.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><p class=\"mt-6 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">ClickTake Technologies was founded to close the gap between strategy, design and engineering. Too many agencies split those disciplines across silos; we built one team that owns the full lifecycle — from the first whiteboard sketch to the post-launch growth experiment that lifts your north-star metric.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><p class=\"mt-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Today we operate from <strong class=\"text-foreground\">Birmingham (UK)</strong>,<strong class=\"text-foreground\"> Lahore (Pakistan)</strong>,<strong class=\"text-foreground\"> Austin (USA)</strong> and<strong class=\"text-foreground\"> Dubai (UAE)</strong>, serving everyone from venture-backed startups to publicly listed groups. Wherever you are in the world, there&#x27;s a ClickTake office in your timezone.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xl\">🇬🇧</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Birmingham</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">United Kingdom</div><div class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground/80 leading-relaxed\">Registered HQ — serving London, Manchester &amp; the Midlands</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xl\">🇵🇰</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Multan</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Pakistan</div><div class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground/80 leading-relaxed\">Engineering &amp; delivery hub — serving Lahore, Karachi, Islamabad &amp; beyond</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xl\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Austin, TX</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">United States</div><div class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground/80 leading-relaxed\">North American business desk — coast to coast coverage</div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl glass p-4 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xl\">🇦🇪</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">Dubai</span></div><div class=\"mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">United Arab Emirates</div><div class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground/80 leading-relaxed\">MENA office — serving Abu Dhabi, Riyadh &amp; Doha</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M7 2v2\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"8\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">AI-native engineering</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">We embed AI into every product we ship — from copilots to fully autonomous workflows — so your business compounds leverage, not headcount.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(64px)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Four-region coverage</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">With teams in Birmingham, Lahore, Austin and Dubai, we deliver 24-hour development cycles and on-the-ground insight in every market we serve.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Enterprise-grade security</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">SOC 2-aligned processes, role-based access, and rigorous code reviews are the default — not an upsell.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(64px)\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-2xl glass p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Ship in weeks, not quarters</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Our AI-assisted delivery pipeline compresses timelines. Most MVPs go live in 8–12 weeks; most marketing sites in 2–4.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto h-px w-full max-w-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-foreground/10 to-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:100% 50% 0\"></div><section id=\"contact\" class=\"relative py-20 sm:py-24 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-1/4 h-[32rem] w-[32rem] rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]/10 blur-[120px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 h-[28rem] w-[28rem] rounded-full bg-[#FF53A9]/10 blur-[120px]\"></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#136DFF]\"></span>Get in touch</div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight\">Let&#x27;s build something<!-- --> <span class=\"gradient-text\">remarkable together.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(48px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Tell us about your project. We typically respond within one business day — and the first 30 minutes of consultation are always on us.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><a href=\"mailto:Info@clicktaketech.com\" class=\"group flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 rounded-2xl glass p-4 sm:p-5 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><div class=\"grid h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground\">Email</div><div class=\"text-sm font-bold group-hover:text-[#136DFF] transition truncate\">Info@clicktaketech.com</div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right ml-auto h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground group-hover:text-foreground transition shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-64px)\"><a href=\"tel:+923069753003\" class=\"group flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 rounded-2xl glass p-4 sm:p-5 hover:border-white/20 transition\"><div class=\"grid h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-xl gradient-bg shadow-